data.name: lblDesc.Text
data.value: The Pomodoro Technique is a time management method developed by Francesco Cirillo. Basicly: Work 25 minutes, rest 5 minutes. You can start this app by clicking the "Pomo!" Button. You can also pause an ongoing pomo interval. After 25 minutes Lazy Pomo suggests to rest 5 minutes. Start a new pomo interval by clicking again the "Pomo!" button.
